---
title: Bison, Mixed Mushroom and Bacon Pie with Spring Salad
description: Mixed mushrooms and savoury bison take centre stage in this mouthwatering pie, with bacon, carrots, peas, rosemary and baby potatoes as their hearty co-stars! A simple spring salad alongside balances out the rich flavours.
